text: Narayanpur Tatwara railway station is a railway station in Sawai Madhopur district, Rajasthan. Its code is NNW. It serves Narayanpur Tatwara. The station consists of 2 platforms. Passenger and Express trains halt here. ==References== Category:Railway stations in Sawai Madhopur district Category:Kota railway division
title: Narayanpur Tatwara railway station
